.Dd June 11, 2025
.Dt PUC 4
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm puc
.Nd PCI
.Dq Universal
Communications driver
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "device pci"
.Cd "device puc"
.Cd "device uart"
.Cd "device ppc"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver acts as a shim to connect
PCI multi-port serial and parallel adapters to the
.Xr uart 4
and
.Xr ppc 4
driver.
